1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,910


2
00:00:03,910 --> 00:00:07,730
Nau mai ki tēnei whakaaturanga a ipurangi o te tēpu,

3
00:00:07,730 --> 00:00:11,020
kei te take kōrero tātou mō Whakaata Māori.

4
00:00:11,020 --> 00:00:16,240
Kei te tutukia rānei te hiahia kia pāho nuitia tō tātou reo rangatira,

5
00:00:16,240 --> 00:00:18,810
kei te pēhea kē rānei?

6
00:00:18,810 --> 00:00:22,580
Kei konei ngā kaikōrero he kaipāpāho katoa.

7
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:27,510
Te Waihoroi Shortland, Stacey Morrison, Eruera Morgan, tēnā koutou,

8
00:00:27,510 --> 00:00:29,460
anei te pātai, Eruera,

9
00:00:29,460 --> 00:00:35,140
mā te ao pāpāho ka ora te reo Māori, pīki tika, pīki teka rānei.

10
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:39,630
Ehara mā te pouaka whakaata Māori anake e ora ai tō tātou reo.

11
00:00:39,630 --> 00:00:40,660
Nā reira pīki teka

12
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:46,840
nā te mea kei te kaha whakapono tātou mā te ao pāpāho ka ora te reo Māori.

13
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:50,470
roa e kōrerohia ana. He aha ō whakaaro,

14
00:00:50,470 --> 00:00:54,290
e ora ana te reo mā te pouaka whakaata Māori.

15
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:55,890
Me pērā taku whakautu.

16
00:00:55,890 --> 00:01:00,550
Engari kaua mā te...Pouaka Whakaata anake.

17
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:07,820
Tekau tau te pakeke, Stacey, tekau tau te pakeke o te teihana kei te whakatinanahia te tūmanako.

18
00:01:07,820 --> 00:01:16,790
Engari, kua eke taumata i ētahi wā, engari me whai tonu i te pae tawhiti, koinā tāku.

19
00:01:16,790 --> 00:01:18,610
Me whiu anō au tēnā pātai.

20
00:01:18,610 --> 00:01:24,170
Mā te ao pāpāho tō tātou reo Māori e ora ai

21
00:01:24,170 --> 00:01:29,020
e kore māna e ora ai.

22
00:01:29,020 --> 00:01:35,830
Māna e noho e kitea whānui ai, e rongohia whānui ai,

23
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:39,440
mā te iwi anake te reo ka ora.

24
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:44,400
Kāhore mā... mā ngā taputapu nei kia...

25
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:47,930
kia manawanui te iwi ki tana reo,

26
00:01:47,930 --> 00:01:57,090
ko te mahi a tēnei Hōngere e whaka piki i taua manawanui.

27
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:59,320
Kāhore i tua atu i tērā

28
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:04,750
kei te eke te mahi a te whakaata Māori  i runga i tēnā whakaaro.

29
00:02:04,750 --> 00:02:07,870
Kei te ahu atu ia i runga i te huarahi tika.

30
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:10,850
Tēnā koe kōrua, koutou māmā.

31
00:02:10,850 --> 00:02:17,310
E hoa mā, hei whakamākūkū i te korokoro te tikanga o tēnei whakaaturanga poto,

32
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:34,858
tēnā kia rangona te roanga atu o ngā kōrero huri mai ki a tēpu haurua o te iwa pō Wenerei Whakaata Māori kia mau ō karu.
